<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.9.6">
<l>poṉmuttu mariyukirum puḻaikkaimmā karikkōṭum</l>
<l>miṉṉattaṇ tiraiyuntum viyaṉpoṉṉit tirunaṟaiyūr</l>
<l>miṉṉotta nuṇmaruṅkul melliyalai tirumārvil</l>
<l>maṉṉattāṉ vaittukantāṉ malaraṭiyē yaṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In Tirunaṟaiyūr where the wide Poṉṉi [River] casts up,</l>
<l rend="indent">in cool waves so they glitter,</l>
<l>Gold, pearls, lion’s claws, and tusks of hollow-trunked huge elephants,</l>
<l>O heart, take refuge at the flower[-like] feet of the one who delights in</l>
<l rend="indent">the soft-natured [lady] with a lightning-like, thin waist,</l>
<l>Keeping [her] at his divine chest so that [she] stays [eternally].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
